      "review_summary": "Adds a built-in SmolVM delegated-run provider with REST lifecycle support, archive sync, CLI/config/env/docs wiring, aliases, registration, and tests, plus a global lease-slug vocabulary change.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review findings: source inspection of the latest PR head shows the unvalidated BaseURL path and the ineffective duplicate json tag for exit_code decoding. The PR’s live proof covers the happy path but does not exercise those failure or unsafe-config cases.",
